{"tid":1726996,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［公投］終於出老解，連登巴絲會唔會返屋企訓？","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T12:17:37.000Z","uid":156509,"like":59,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"786e4aa12ea8f4c0f5c8300d8921075ec0279937","tid":1726996,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNMVaWc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNMVaWc.png&h=35509cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日終於出咗老解「自發」清理路障，<br />\n連登巴絲會唔會因此返屋企訓覺？<br />\n<br />\n唔會，攬炒目標未達成，鎮壓先再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會，好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959745246b428a7309dd3c13264d687b32ac39bf","tid":1726996,"uid":156509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"老解你老母，解放军就解放军啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT5VVoS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT5VVoS.png&h=2f4fbf8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2748d0a3c9e11e20a515975bb4c7303ab6d62fa8","tid":1726996,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"我地要做既係美國戰線阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地藍屍撐由佢地，佢係係咪都奶共架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大件事 唔好玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國會美中經濟與安全審議委員會發表年度報告，表示若果中國對香港出動解放軍或武警干預香港局勢，美國國會應該撤銷《美國-香港政策法》給予香港獨立關稅區的特殊地位。"},{"pid":"6cb7dd46fa259df29572feb6f0ab234ca51e9f56","tid":1726996,"uid":156509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日清路障，聽日開真槍</span></span>"},{"pid":"40ec7f7bb83f01a9dc8bffb305abb346a57a61d8","tid":1726996,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:04:13.000Z","msg":"未正式出"},{"pid":"77c65ecd20197403c6ce8c6b463c801242f4d2be","tid":1726996,"uid":156509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"40ec7f7bb83f01a9dc8bffb305abb346a57a61d8","tid":1726996,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:04:13.000Z","msg":"未正式出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"咁暗地裏出嘅話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc3727734c5d422d835ace7ee623c8d44202c54","tid":1726996,"uid":156509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:16:41.000Z","msg":"終於出老解！&hellip;你不會真的相信他們是「自發」吧？<br />\n<br />\n終於出老解！大家可以返屋企訓覺～<br />\n<br />\n講完笑，回正題，解放軍聲稱，今次是「自發」出動協助清理路障，協助「止暴制亂」（其實上次打風都「自發」過一次）。<br />\n<br />\n問題：解放軍駐港部隊，是否真的可以突然「自發」殺出軍營？<br />\n<br />\n答案：不可以，理論上。<br />\n<br />\n根據《駐軍法》，駐港解放軍的職務包括「抵抗侵略」、「防衛勤務」、「管理軍事設施」、「承辦涉外軍事」，若全國人大決定「宣布戰爭狀態」，或者出現一些特區政府不能控制、危及國家統安全的動亂，決定香港進入「緊急狀態」，解放軍就可以履行職責－<br />\n<br />\n否則，「香港駐軍不干預香港特別行政區的地方事務」，當然，解放軍的職務，不包括在九龍塘清垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n而即使他們職務包括執垃圾，第一，香港不是戰爭狀態，第二香港不是緊急狀態，亦無解放軍出動的條件。<br />\n<br />\n還有一個例外，就是香港政府在「必要時」，向中央請求駐港解放軍協助救助災害，中央批准後，由中央軍委下令出動，任務完成後返回軍營。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府提出、中央批准、軍委下令，千看萬看，就是沒有「自發」出來這回事。<br />\n<br />\n原因？主權移交之初，解放軍可是被視為洪水猛獸們，最好一直躲在軍營閉門不出。<br />\n<br />\n今天解放軍出來執磚，當然可以一笑置之，但這些行動背後的訊息，就是曾經將解放軍鎖在軍營的基本法、駐軍法，以至公眾觀感，概括就是：公關，對中共而言愈來愈不是一回事，日後解放軍「自發」甚至獲命做甚麼，看來也不用太奇怪。<br />\n<br />\nbtw，你不會真的相信他們是「自發」吧？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019/11/16 - 18:03 林彥邦<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/終於出老解-你不會真的相信他們是-自發-吧/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E5%87%BA%E8%80%81%E8%A7%A3-%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%96%E5%80%91%E6%98%AF-%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BC-%E5%90%A7%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXnjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=a8636d53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E5%87%BA%E8%80%81%E8%A7%A3-%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%96%E5%80%91%E6%98%AF-%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BC-%E5%90%A7%2F&h=69e6f4b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/終於出老解-你不會真的相信他們是-自發-吧/</a>"},{"pid":"cc47c651abb81d6cd4b51acf033bff65097c941f","tid":1726996,"uid":52090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"今日「自發」執磚，明日「自發」<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屠城</span></span><br />\n<br />\n解放軍正式管理香港政治，<br />\n以後會有「自發」解放軍<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">管理選舉及遊行</span>"},{"pid":"b9a8de172f7b65d56c20b6cd56b3107b8cf3311b","tid":1726996,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"959745246b428a7309dd3c13264d687b32ac39bf","tid":1726996,"uid":156509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"老解你老母，解放军就解放军啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT5VVoS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT5VVoS.png&h=2f4fbf8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:17:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cac0a05b744d2aa8db3191909f724559037e3c1","tid":1726996,"uid":336561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"唔可以當冇事發生過<br />\n岀老解係件好嚴重既事<br />\n今次係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試水溫</span></span>"},{"pid":"c07c1d3d617452c0174b07619cfd886f2993bb62","tid":1726996,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"77c65ecd20197403c6ce8c6b463c801242f4d2be","tid":1726996,"uid":156509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"40ec7f7bb83f01a9dc8bffb305abb346a57a61d8","tid":1726996,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1